snippet.title: Funniest ICE CREAM moments! - Another DAILY DOSE of LAUGHING for you!
snippet.description:
It is summer time and we are all ice cream lovers, aren't we :D Here are few funniest moments, happened in last few yeares, which may improve your daily mood ;) Funniest and cutest fails collected for you! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
